{"tid":1105534,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(感情+心事+音樂台) 召集一眾巴絲打入嚟傾計","createTime":"2019-04-14T03:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-15T02:22:38.000Z","uid":43718,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e54c17ff85fb43b7e665ca805433ba6bd59186f0","tid":1105534,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T03:39:42.000Z","msg":"最近發現Discord原來有個bot可以一路播歌 一路傾計<br />\n<br />\n咁啱小弟喺外國身邊又無咩做 所以想睇下有無巴絲打同我一樣<br />\n<br />\n咁啱無咩嘢做 又想搵嘢聽下 咪入黎傾下計吹下水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果巴絲打有心事感情學業工作煩惱都可以係度分享 睇下咁其他巴打有無咩意見畀到你咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n得閒仲可以點下歌開心share大家音樂既興趣 無聊想廢up下都得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最緊要係要禁入嚟睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n而家已經有接近70個巴絲打入咗頻道啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今晚2330左右開台 主題會圍繞「中學往事」方面<br />\n<br />\n當然你有其他嘢想傾 都無任歡迎<br />\n<br />\n有興趣就入嚟聽聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n傳送門: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/qFTfqpc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FqFTfqpc&d=3CWkRSL9Alw2F84R5nIU8qjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=5d582e54\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/qFTfqpc</a>"},{"pid":"d691e8a6632e3dcc38dc288d1660760b5e9856b9","tid":1105534,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T03:40:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc689d541459b1c5237ced2c5e725fceb2122b7d","tid":1105534,"uid":43718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T03:46:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1fb9c817988f6750f966f3270e5f46c80fafc